Package: SIRA
Type: Package
Title: Scalable Image-on-Scalar Regression Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ralph", "Jiang", email = "ralphjia@umich.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits image-on-scalar regression models with spatially homogeneous,
    sparse coefficient images. The Scalable Image-on-Scalar Regression
    Algorithm (SIRA) uses a coordinate-descent procedure with five region
    operations (expand, shrink, revalue, merge, split) and precomputed summary
    statistics to scale to high-dimensional neuroimaging data.
